description: No this is not a behind-the-scene, it is even better! For the first time, you get access to the rawfootages of our classic scenes! Meaning that you see the entire takes, exactly as they were shot before editing. I find it exciting because you really feel as if you were there in the roomwith us. That's reality at its best!
title: Raw Footages - Ricky's Peep Show, Scene #01
